2038	  \emph{Literature.} Stacks Tag~\textbf{02KH} (cohomology along proper morphisms commutes with flat base change); Stacks Tag~\textbf{0AY8} (integral closure descends under flat base change); Hartshorne III.9.3 (flat base change of cohomology, the $H^0$ row).
2039	\end{proof}
